belItem">...more</span></button></div></ul></div><div class="BookDetails"><div class="CollapsableList"><span class="Text Text__body3"><div class="FeaturedDetails"><p data-testid="pagesFormat">158 pages, Paperback</p><p data-testid="publicationInfo">First published January 1, 1993</p><p data-testid="awards"><span class="CollapsableList"><span data-testid="award"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/award/show/5346-lambda-literary-award">Lambda Literary Award</a>, Drama<span class="Text Text__subdued"> (1995)</span></span></span></p></div></span> <div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--inline Button--small" aria-label="Show more book details"><span class="Button__labelItem">More details</span></button></div></div></div><hr class="Divider" role="presentation"/><div class="AuthorPreview"><div class="AuthorPreview__profile"><div class="AuthorPreview__avatar"><a class="Avatar Avatar--large" href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/35822.Tony_Kushner" as="div"><img data-testid="image" class="Avatar__image" alt="Tony Kushner" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/authors/1209471902i/35822._UX200_CR0,40,200,200_.jpg"/></a></div><div class="AuthorPreview__info"><h3 class="Text H3"><a class="ContributorLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/35822.Tony_Kushner"><span class="ContributorLink__name" data-testid="name">Tony Kushner</span></a></h3><div class="AuthorPreview__meta"><span class="Text Text__body3 Text__subdued">67<!-- --> <!-- -->books<span class="u-dot-before">382<!-- --> <!-- -->followers</span></span></div></div></div><div class="TruncatedText"><div class="TruncatedText__text TruncatedText__text--3" data-testid="contentContainer"><div><span class="Formatted">Tony Kushner is an award-winning American playwright most famous for his play <i>Angels in America</i>, for which he was awarded the Pulitzer Prize. He is also co-author, along with Eric Roth, of the screenplay of the 2005 film <i>Munic